<h4 id="concept">Concept</h4>
<ol>
  <li>\hsize: horizontal size is a TeX primitive that should not be usually used in Latex.</li>
  <li>\textwidth: the constant width of the total text block.</li>
  <li>\columnwidth the constant width of a single column of test.</li>
  <li>\linewidth is a variable that represents the current size of the line of text.
    <ul>
      <li>\linewidth may changed in a nested list, \hsize, \testwidth, \columnwidth donâ€™t change.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

